txt.en: 'Leave this foe to me. I will break them.'
'You dare stand against the Anâkhi? We must stop them from reaching Nâkhugir!'
'I still stand and you will not reach Nâkhugir!'
'Kizurdâl, no! You will pay for this!'
'You should not have come here. You will go no deeper into Ashunûg!'
Ashunûg, the Fane of the Accursed
